Package: HexSampleR
Title: Create Sample Points For Polygon(s)
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Robert",
           family = "McGaughey",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "robert.mcgaughey@usda.gov")
Description: HexSampleR generates a set of sample points contained within a polygon feature(s).
  Given an input polygon(s), HexSampleR creates a set of sample points within the polygon. 
  Multi-part polygons are allowed. The number of sample points will be distributed over the parts.
